trans-unit.source: Represents a version of the .NET Framework where an application can install and run.
trans-unit.target: 表示.NET Framework 应用程序可以在其中安装和运行的版本。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the profile of the .NET Framework version where an application can install and run.
trans-unit.target: 指定应用程序可以在其中安装和运行的.NET Framework 版本的配置文件。

trans-unit.source: If the .NET Framework version is [!INCLUDE[net_client_v40_long](~/add/includes/net-client-v40-long-md.md)], the Profile property returns "Client".
trans-unit.target: 如果.NET Framework 版本[!INCLUDE[net_client_v40_long](~/add/includes/net-client-v40-long-md.md)]，该配置文件属性返回"客户端"。

trans-unit.source: If the .NET Framework version is [!INCLUDE[net_v40_long](~/add/includes/net-v40-long-md.md)], the Profile property returns "Full".
trans-unit.target: 如果.NET Framework 版本[!INCLUDE[net_v40_long](~/add/includes/net-v40-long-md.md)]，该配置文件属性返回"Full"。

trans-unit.source: A string that represents the profile.
trans-unit.target: 一个字符串，表示配置文件。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the runtime version number of the .NET Framework where an application can install and run.
trans-unit.target: 指定.NET Framework 应用程序可以在其中安装和运行的运行时版本号。

trans-unit.source: New versions of the .NET Framework may operate on previously-released versions of the runtime.
trans-unit.target: 新版本的.NET Framework 可以在以前发布的运行时版本上运行。

trans-unit.source: A string that represents the runtime version.
trans-unit.target: 一个字符串，表示运行时版本。
